quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,And/by the night when/if it covers/darkens
  92,2,And/by the daytime when/if it uncovered/shined
  92,3,And/by what (who) created the male and the female
  92,4,That truly your striving/endeavor (is) separate/different (E)
  92,5,So but who gave/granted and feared and obeyed
  92,6,And gave charity/confirmed with the best/most beautiful
  92,7,So We will ease him to the ease/prosperity
  92,8,And but who was stingy/miser and sufficed/availed
  92,9,And lied/denied/falsified with the best/most beautiful
  92,10,So We will ease him to the difficulty/hardship
  92,11,And his property/possession/wealth does not enrich/suffice (replace) from him if he fell/was destroyed
  92,12,That truly on Us (is) the guidance (E)
  92,13,"And that truly for Us (is) the end (other life) (E), and the first/beginning"
  92,14,And so I warned you/gave you notice (of) a fire blazing/burning/inflaming
  92,15,None roasts/suffers it except the most miserable/unhappy
  92,16,Who lied/denied/falsified and turned away
  92,17,And the most fearing and obeying will be made to avoid it/be distanced from it
  92,18,Who gives/brings his property/possession/wealth (and) purifies/corrects (himself)
  92,19,And (there) is not to anyone at Him from a blessing/goodness to be rewarded/reimbursed
  92,20,Except wishing/desiring his Lord`s the highest`s/mightiest`s/most dignified`s face/front (path)
  92,21,And he/He will/shall (E) accept/approve